     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">I</seg> Wish thee conscience and care in rea<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ding and follow<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ing what is contai<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ned in the ensuing Sermons; which are now more large in the Presse then they were in the Pulpit, and may receive a farther addition of certaine cases if leasure shall permit, in meane time let this that is done profit thee, and helpe him with thy prayers who is thine in the best bond and ready to doe thee good,</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>JO: SEDGVVICK.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
